      <title>日本央行可能透過新的價格預測暗示近期升息</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/bank-japan-may-signal-near-term-rate-hike-with-new-price-forecasts-2024-04-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行週五預計，未來幾年通膨率將保持在 2% 的目標附近，並表示準備將利率從接近零的水平上調，以防止日圓空頭將日圓推至 34 年來新低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/bank-japan-may-signal-near-term-rate-hike-with-new-price-forecasts-2024-04-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 22:25:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
