      <title>日圓存在日本央行無法輕易解決的殖利率問題</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-has-yield-problem-boj-cant-easily-fix-2024-04-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[隨著日圓跌至三年來的低點，日本幹預或改變貨幣政策的壓力越來越大，交易員認為，東京無法採取太多措施來扭轉日圓貶值，而利率和勢頭嚴重不利於日圓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-has-yield-problem-boj-cant-easily-fix-2024-04-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 09:30:47 GMT</pubDate>
